title: Nobody Wants to Tell Trump He Lost 11.6.20
itunes:title: Nobody Wants to Tell Trump He Lost 11.6.20
description:
In episode 754, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Blair Socci to discuss the 2020 election results, what if Trump won't concede, who will tell Trump to wrap it up, the nation diversifying faster than predicted, the most ordered food from election week, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. 2020 Election: Live Results And Coverage
  2. What is a US presidential candidate refuses to concede after an election? 
  3. Will Jared or Ivanka tell Trump to go?President's inner circle search for someone brave (or dumb) enough to tell him it's over as he 'prepares to hold a "victory" rally this weekend'
  4. The nation is diversifying even faster than predicted, according to new census data
  5. ELECTION DAY 2020 PIZZA & MARGARITAS REIGN SUPREME For Voters Watching Results
  6. WATCH: Slidecamp - Realmsweeper
